of 0.85 percentage point above the Treasury's 10-year note.
Rated double-A-1 by Moody's and double-A-minus by S&amp;P, the
issue will be sold through underwriters led by Kidder,
Peabody &amp; Co. The multilateral agency extends loans to
African nations.
                                                                                                       

