   Investor's Amrep Stake
   Almost Doubles as Bid
   For Board Discussed
</HL>
<DATE>
06/20/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   AXR
