<IN>
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
PETROLEUM (PET)
</IN>
<LP>
   Freeport McMoRan Resource Partners L.P. said it and joint
venture partners acquired from Chevron U.S.A. Inc., for $137
million, reserves estimated at 35 million to 50 million
barrels of oil and eight billion cubic feet of natural gas.
An additional $13 million will be paid to Chevron for costs
already incurred.
